edu.dynamic.dynamiz.parser

Class Options

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.dynamic.dynamiz.parser.Options

  • public class Options
extends java.lang.Object
    List of Options This is a container of Option. Multiple Option of the same OptionType will be grouped together.

    Provide utility methods to check for ambiguity if one OptionType has more than one occurrence.

    Author:
    nhan

      • add

        public boolean add(java.util.List<Option> optList)
        Add a list of Option. The OptionType of the list will have to be the same for all the elements. Otherwise, the operation will return false and nothing will be added to Options collection.
        Parameters:
        optList - the list of Option to be added
        Returns:
        true if the list of Option is of the same OptionType and successfully added to the collection. False otherwise.
